data.description: Southern Charm meets the Cooper river. Located on a tidal creek within Pimlico, enjoy the perks of quiet living and seconds to the Cooper river. With a large wrap around porch, dock and a public kayak/canoe launch the watersports are there to enjoy year round.  At 3694 sqft, there's space for entertaining both inside and outside. The family room and dining room have high ceilings and natural light. The kitchen provides lots of counter space along with custom cabinets and built-ins. The sunroom and porch allows you to relax at any time of the day. This home also has an outdoor shower and sink, perfect for cleaning up after a long day outside.Civic Center is located at the front of neighborhood.Buyer to verify any and all information deemed necessaryMOTIVATED SELLERS, submit allOptional HOA fee that is $25 Annually which allows access to rent the Civic Center. There is also a one time $125 key fee that allows access to the boat landing.
